\f1\b \cf0 Downhill landing
\f0\b0 . Be mindful to not overshoot.\
\
Punctually, the park will have 
\f1\b sheep
\f0\b0  graze on vegetation for maintenance purposes. Do not land with the sheep when they are present.\
\
To avoid landing in the avocado orchad and make it to the main LZ, you need to leave the spine high enough. \
